column5: Been going down to the pier yesterday and today,action is slow haven't seen a perch yet.some guy got a nice rainbow my buddy bartlett got a nice pike and so did some people further out. The ice is a bit sketchy though especially after today.
Thanks for the report, I hope to get out there soon for some pike... Are Pier 4 and Bayfront referring to the same park?  Burt
yes siry bob.but there is a nice place around the corner for monster pike.
